    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏详情</h2>这是一款能让玩家在空中自由翱翔的狩猎系动作RPG。<br><br>与灵梦和魔理沙从上空攻击敌人，把敌人一一摧毁吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◎战斗系统</h2><br>◆正常攻击<br>正常攻击有「格斗」以及「射击」的两种。<br>命中格斗攻击将会让您积累射击能量。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/27d4554461e27383a6795a0b0f16b74c.poster.avif?t=1710782124\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/27d4554461e27383a6795a0b0f16b74c.webm?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/27d4554461e27383a6795a0b0f16b74c.mp4?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>◆符卡<br>命中射击攻击会让您积累符卡能量。<br>积累符卡能量，发挥「符卡」的力量，以华美的弹幕彻底地压倒敌人吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/0494124c4064c7729084c10c1bc3473d.poster.avif?t=1710782124\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/0494124c4064c7729084c10c1bc3473d.webm?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/0494124c4064c7729084c10c1bc3473d.mp4?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>◆擦弹<br>恰到好处地躲避敌人的攻击叫做「擦弹」。<br>「擦弹」可以帮您积累射击能量<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/d8f57d6a13a2ddff1a0017163c425ee3.poster.avif?t=1710782124\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/d8f57d6a13a2ddff1a0017163c425ee3.webm?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/d8f57d6a13a2ddff1a0017163c425ee3.mp4?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>◆部位破坏<br>敌人身上会有可以破坏的部位。<br>部位破坏成功会助您获取用于制造武器的材料。<br>积极地破坏敌人身上的部位，收集材料吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/81d4262c67c9f1b7870f53ae7da4f1c7.poster.avif?t=1710782124\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/81d4262c67c9f1b7870f53ae7da4f1c7.webm?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/81d4262c67c9f1b7870f53ae7da4f1c7.mp4?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◎装备系统</h2>您可以用所得到的材料强化装备。<br><br>装备的强化会使符卡受到强化，使符卡变得更加华美。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/b7294671c5030487b068f8ea2d0b3c25.avif?t=1710782124\" width=480 height=270 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◎故事情节</h2>在幻想乡突然冒出来的侵略兵器「金属蜘蛛」。<br>恐怖的侵略兵器竟然来自于人类村落！？<br>灵梦和魔理沙为了解决异变赶向人类村落，竟然发现…<br><br>・故事中登场的角色全都会采用Live2D呈现。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/5503afcf70f6bb6a5ff101eb7273995f.poster.avif?t=1710782124\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/5503afcf70f6bb6a5ff101eb7273995f.webm?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/5503afcf70f6bb6a5ff101eb7273995f.mp4?t=1710782124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>故事虽然是「东方铃奈庵」和「东方绀珠传」的后日谈，但是即使不了解之前剧情也能充分地享受故事的精彩内容。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◎键盘操作设置</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/1a5c5acbe41a38b873b9593a83ae7781.avif?t=1710782124\" width=486 height=274 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222050/extras/ab0c84b2d09c370709bfe8d1b411bf29.avif?t=1710782124\" width=486 height=274 /></span>",
